column5: Anyone used any of Andrew Martensens products?   Any thoughts?
His name is spelled Martinsen. I guess that's a secret too.
Nice.  Sorry about the spelling error, but in all seriousness is any of his products worth it?

57 bucks  Try going to the library and getting a book it`s free!!! or for limited time only send me 47 buck and I`ll send you Gord Harris`s Walleye fishing secrets and as a bonus I will throw in a Banjo minnow!!!

I seriously have to look into setting up a e-commerce web site and start peddling this crap to the masses,there seems to be quite a demand for this stuff!!!  Anybody know how much it costs to set up a e-commerce website?

Dont buy it ,, you are getting  great advice here,, i get emails from him all the time ,i think 5 times a week ,just look at the free vids they send or the odd free ebook ,just teasers but heh ,why pay for it ,everyone knows that the fish are in the water ,,.
